Package viewModel

Class WelcomeViewViewModel

java.lang.Object
viewModel.WelcomeViewViewModel
public class WelcomeViewViewModel
extends java.lang.Object
View Model for the initial Welcome Screen. The class receives the username from WelcomeView and passes it on to the Client Constructor. If the name is available, a new Client is created and the ChatView is initialized.
Author:
Josef, Elias
